Program: Discovery
Title: Treating cancer
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrws0
Last Broadcast Date: 25 November 1996
Should medical science be changing its approach to treating cancer? Three experts believe it is time to re-think how tumours are dealt with. Also in the programme, the comings and goings of our ancestors, quick clean chemistry and an adult-only item, the sex lives of ladybirds.